                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220703-43-off228 t18220703-43-cd229"></join>, one watch, value 50 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220703-43-victim423" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
